                <item type="txt" lang="tau">ch'ale</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="d86c7940-533e-4e11-ba78-6a354646db7e">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">agndeel</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">,"</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="b8062577-b1a9-45f3-b233-d01a2f468d1b">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">udihnih</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">.</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">"Yes, as for me, I eat them," I told him.</item>
          </phrase>
        </phrases>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph guid="e7020d01-cf7f-4f87-be88-fed5a5cf0d86">
        <phrases>
          <phrase guid="956d48ea-4314-4ad2-9b60-3cf12ed1f267">
            <item type="txt" lang="tau">K'at'eey minaniich'akthädn eh ay du' agnthäł nts'ą̈' t'eey uu'akdiih ch'ale.</item>
            <item type="segnum" lang="en">44</item>
            <words>
              <word guid="46233a8b-5c3c-4886-b013-a2aac85dd409">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">K'at'eey</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="c2406fee-8894-48dc-8f7c-183b8df7a9d9">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">minaniich'akthädn</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="c9b84ef9-2e6f-4655-b1e3-36d63121e151">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">eh</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="4bfc32f1-e921-4f77-b157-0e5e605fc31b">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">ay</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="8f8da878-6648-4c0d-b61b-8a1db78a468b">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">du'</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="3edc6df8-0f31-47dd-a45e-d5c24f4fbda4">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">agnthäł</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="8f4292e9-703a-4dbe-8d5b-73a277d7534c">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">nts'ą̈'</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="edbd6f02-700d-430c-9c6b-d9f24b83f3c4">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">t'eey</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="d6014f9e-6265-4675-a769-b46ba6996ef2">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">uu'akdiih</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="bc4089da-4d1d-477d-be74-cb9a09f3da8a">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">ch'ale</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">.</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">I didn't even think about it; I was running and then I was shooting it.</item>
          </phrase>
        </phrases>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph guid="a0380684-b9fc-4e60-9356-11e6d29a2850">
        <phrases>
          <phrase guid="05ddb1de-999b-40f6-bb1c-00179517b960">
            <item type="txt" lang="tau">Ch'itay du' k'at'eey minaniich'akthädn.</item>
            <item type="segnum" lang="en">45</item>
            <words>
              <word guid="3e2cdf88-1c10-482d-8fee-f4324f393a9c">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">Ch'itay</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="8f8da878-6648-4c0d-b61b-8a1db78a468b">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">du'</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="7f2bfe42-7e9b-4e4d-9dc5-7a9fbad30cdf">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">k'at'eey</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="c2406fee-8894-48dc-8f7c-183b8df7a9d9">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">minaniich'akthädn</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">.</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">I wasn't thinking about that old man though.</item>
          </phrase>
        </phrases>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph guid="5e7c4e09-8bb5-4c66-aede-bc3455e6a068">
        <phrases>
          <phrase guid="bc3df42f-064f-4924-8901-548d76e92461">
            <item type="txt" lang="tau">Shuudehka:::t.</item>
            <item type="segnum" lang="en">46</item>
            <words>
              <word guid="289c18c4-0b3f-489b-be03-b59a17c88f7e">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">Shuudehka</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">:::</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="934a6333-7ccf-4b81-b19d-c48bb3c80da8">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">t</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">.</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">He kept asking me questions.</item>
          </phrase>
        </phrases>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph guid="905c03a4-6bc0-4466-ad3a-de29a100700a">
        <phrases>
          <phrase guid="1f5110a8-9b06-402b-b915-1f04f69f5113">
            <item type="txt" lang="tau">"Nday? </item>
            <item type="segnum" lang="en">47.1</item>
            <words>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">"</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="c3db526e-e6d1-460c-97f6-40ac0390331f">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">Nday</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">?</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">"Where?</item>
          </phrase>
          <phrase guid="ac36b2a7-1ddd-4d36-9487-e6c28ca7e6a9">
            <item type="txt" lang="tau">Nday?"</item>
            <item type="segnum" lang="en">47.2</item>
            <words>
              <word guid="c3db526e-e6d1-460c-97f6-40ac0390331f">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">Nday</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">?"</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">Where?"</item>
          </phrase>
        </phrases>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph guid="d79180f3-09d2-4cfc-9e08-eb12afa21787">
        <phrases>
          <phrase guid="f68943fa-68fb-430e-a69a-d0672090f31e">
            <item type="txt" lang="tau">"Ndee nushyign', tamaagn nts'ą̈' nushyign' tu tth'itu' nts'ą̈' tah shoh eedah."</item>
            <item type="segnum" lang="en">48</item>
            <words>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">"</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="42eb34c6-88e3-49fb-ad01-8075d98eda53">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">Ndee</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="358bf4a1-3c6f-439a-9986-9513d3eb2733">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">nushyign'</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">,</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="db2398ec-a67b-4cec-b69d-506ee87d934f">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">tamaagn</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="8f4292e9-703a-4dbe-8d5b-73a277d7534c">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">nts'ą̈'</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="358bf4a1-3c6f-439a-9986-9513d3eb2733">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">nushyign'</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="97ed9bd7-743d-497e-9dc0-3f54c8605a38">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">tu</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="6ad2d6b1-6131-460f-9191-a3313060c5c3">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">tth'itu'</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="8f4292e9-703a-4dbe-8d5b-73a277d7534c">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">nts'ą̈'</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="ec98ad2e-f253-41b6-9c3f-6feb734e751f">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">tah</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="79a1157b-6a4d-4e96-9a58-ea3b1dcb3982">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">shoh</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="9e6f17da-b146-4b70-980a-af838b082fb0">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">eedah</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">."</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">"Way down there, at the water's edge, by the river, the bear is sitting."</item>
          </phrase>
        </phrases>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph guid="502e9aec-05d6-40b4-a535-290a2a46316b">
        <phrases>
          <phrase guid="6f83abbc-c947-437d-8f7c-d868f0e53e5c">
            <item type="txt" lang="tau">"Maa ni'uhshya' nts'ą̈' nok-'įį!" </item>
            <item type="segnum" lang="en">49.1</item>
            <words>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">"</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="73cb9840-a646-4945-a325-d266ebbb8d91">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">Maa</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="ade48957-cc08-4e76-aead-9927805e4f26">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">ni'uhshya'</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="8f4292e9-703a-4dbe-8d5b-73a277d7534c">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">nts'ą̈'</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="92f0a1b1-a207-49ba-a244-1f44caad525c">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">nok</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">-</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="a6b87883-6180-4234-b475-85a4a198afac">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">'įį</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">!"</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">"I want to go there and see it!"</item>
          </phrase>
          <phrase guid="e8c0e8bf-2e9d-4b86-accd-cd6e443e3a92">
            <item type="txt" lang="tau">nih.</item>
            <item type="segnum" lang="en">49.2</item>
            <words>
              <word guid="820431fc-5475-4802-b57d-8716411f77b9">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">nih</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">.</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">he said.</item>
          </phrase>
        </phrases>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph guid="563414ac-e0c7-41b9-9f6e-f36f8175af6b">
        <phrases>
          <phrase guid="78e68027-90b7-48e8-b7e9-7fc0aa81638e">
            <item type="txt" lang="tau">"Ayt'oo, ayt'oo," udihnih.</item>
            <item type="segnum" lang="en">50</item>
            <words>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">"</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="f6e577c3-538f-4157-bbf4-5ed265fae2e4">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">Ayt'oo</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">,</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="84d79b19-1c04-49ca-bd55-9977a81370f1">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">ayt'oo</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">,"</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="b8062577-b1a9-45f3-b233-d01a2f468d1b">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">udihnih</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">.</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">"It's alright, it's alright," I tell him.</item>
          </phrase>
        </phrases>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph guid="bfe1bf8c-f4e8-4f54-9f3f-f996b432f982">
        <phrases>
          <phrase guid="b1a2fe5a-188b-436c-8802-3acc72d183d1">
            <item type="txt" lang="tau">Nushyign' tah ts'aahaal.</item>
            <item type="segnum" lang="en">51</item>
            <words>
              <word guid="6bfe6548-36c4-4d2b-90cc-ee7a71861194">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">Nushyign'</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="ec98ad2e-f253-41b6-9c3f-6feb734e751f">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">tah</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="0b993442-ef8f-4557-8395-9cddb0f6d23a">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">ts'aahaal</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">.</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">The two of us are walking down there.</item>
          </phrase>
        </phrases>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph guid="3372eeab-b815-4f32-9544-fb8720344c07">
        <phrases>
          <phrase guid="910acecd-094f-4d81-94a0-b135c22a07c3">
            <item type="txt" lang="tau">Howard iin du' nushyign' tah hiik'anehta'.</item>
            <item type="segnum" lang="en">52</item>
            <words>
              <word guid="e76654df-a5af-4e6d-947d-31ac32819b00">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">Howard</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="31b9e81b-c963-4beb-8852-420905a52a8a">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">iin</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="8f8da878-6648-4c0d-b61b-8a1db78a468b">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">du'</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="358bf4a1-3c6f-439a-9986-9513d3eb2733">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">nushyign'</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="ec98ad2e-f253-41b6-9c3f-6feb734e751f">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">tah</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="614796c9-f524-40f7-b117-879403e62cad">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">hiik'anehta'</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">.</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">Howard and the others down there are taking care of it.</item>
          </phrase>
        </phrases>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph guid="7a06cda4-fab6-48e6-b9d6-0863fac6fec5">
        <phrases>
          <phrase guid="d44df747-601d-4ffe-bbc2-dfe557574076">
            <item type="txt" lang="tau">&lt;Ay&gt; ch'itay eh huxah ninįįshyah tl'aan nduugn nts'ą' natetshyah le' ishyiit nts'ą', k'at'eey udakkadn.</item>
            <item type="segnum" lang="en">53</item>
            <words>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">&lt;</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="9b953d27-8615-43cd-9018-c98779428446">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">Ay</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">&gt;</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="735389de-6741-493b-aace-58160ee8bc45">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">ch'itay</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="c9b84ef9-2e6f-4655-b1e3-36d63121e151">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">eh</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="0f131f1a-5bf0-4451-adf2-dbf0941941a3">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">huxah</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="ef202e74-7bb0-4528-86fe-5e8537b3d926">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">ninįįshyah</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="3a8d4e9e-438f-4142-906f-78a1fca23b60">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">tl'aan</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="3484b7c0-cc46-4286-a9fb-90e003b1c699">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">nduugn</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="b5f88f83-c100-4d2b-9a0b-fc1a4bba1d4d">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">nts'ą'</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="64ba1ed5-87b3-48a9-8ba2-4d36b8dd0e38">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">natetshyah</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="0b5a91a0-72c2-4787-b000-85708d9a5624">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">le'</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="fc667181-e5de-434a-8129-d36dc82fb31d">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">ishyiit</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="b5f88f83-c100-4d2b-9a0b-fc1a4bba1d4d">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">nts'ą'</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">,</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="7f2bfe42-7e9b-4e4d-9dc5-7a9fbad30cdf">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">k'at'eey</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="80ab5785-6568-4a8e-87ef-8bb7bb032ae6">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">udakkadn</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">.</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">And that old man is walking up to them and I don't know where he went from there, I didn't ask.</item>
          </phrase>
        </phrases>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph guid="2760efd3-1329-4b89-a285-451ed023eaef">
        <phrases>
          <phrase guid="3234637f-d649-499a-8996-46c2ac48c755">
            <item type="txt" lang="tau">Ayt'oo t'axoh.</item>
            <item type="segnum" lang="en">54</item>
            <words>
              <word guid="f6e577c3-538f-4157-bbf4-5ed265fae2e4">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">Ayt'oo</item>
              </word>
              <word guid="37531f34-dbc4-4cdb-b02e-78cbfb4a3fe4">
                <item type="txt" lang="tau">t'axoh</item>
              </word>
              <word>
                <item type="punct" lang="tau">.</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">That's it.</item>
          </phrase>
        </phrases>
      </paragraph>
    </paragraphs>
